{"tid":1783981,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"有黑警，冇財神 - 李碧華","createTime":"2019-12-15T10:05:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-15T10:44:07.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"76fd9362cdb5e2bd7570e9dce466117f6eef5988","tid":1783981,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T10:05:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20191215/20825187/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191215%2F20825187%2F&d=WfKWFoUFzWEJR7ioTMJgWvDXWQKahOldmH8%2Bpia8yKE%3D&h=dcfacde0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191215%2F20825187%2F&h=df286294\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20191215/20825187/</a><br />\n<br />\n有黑警，冇財神 - 李碧華<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20191215/large/1576312986_a3c5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20191215%2Flarge%2F1576312986_a3c5.jpg&h=26d07606&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港高登討論區圖片(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港好些熱鬧地區，夜市都冷清清，早前黨鐵與黑警勾結，隨時停駛，重創飲食業零售業，市民減少出外消費，現今只是稍為改善，仍一片蕭條景象，到處都有「執笠」商舖，數千人丟飯碗食穀種，找新工更難。<br />\n<br />\n銀行每隔一兩年都與客戶作問卷調查，了解投資風險承受度。有損友道：「問完計分，銀行驚詫，怎麼成了『最保守』一族？」──有什麼好驚詫，就算再積極的，今時今日只有撤資、移民，還投資？對政府及時局不信任，港人或將回復到把錢放月餅盒中藏於床底了。<br />\n<br />\n這一陣信箱常充斥設計精美推銷卡，多為倫敦大阪泰國台北新加坡&hellip;&hellip;的樓盤，還有免費講座。其他的聖誕禮遇新年特惠，商品吸引且相宜，可惜「賤物鬥窮人」，那些珠寶節名袋展，奢侈品搵鬼去。<br />\n<br />\n──不止「心情」問題，是山埃催淚毒氣中，大家對「沒有明天」的恐慌，爛班子怎收拾殘局？百年不遇的淪落，我們都被選中，遇上了。<br />\n<br />\n新春賀年歌是「防暴到防暴到 黑警多恐怖 防暴話防暴話 冧巴不透露 防暴到防暴到 好走快兩步 一俾佢睇到你 你變暴徒 全港滿警察 椒氣未停 圍捕你多黑暗 不准發聲&hellip;&hellip;」香港已無《財神到》。 <br />\n<br />\n李碧華<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com"},{"pid":"58fdff3b01752b2382fdee747680a9fe5aa2bfc5","tid":1783981,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T10:07:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FDHdKiw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFDHdKiw.jpg&h=779c8437&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NTntx6h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNTntx6h.jpg&h=228c1213&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"de782d5977b52c0c11ddf66de08e83d9da8ff132","tid":1783981,"uid":202524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T10:44:07.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 借個位黎<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">德國戰線要人</span></span><br />\n<br />\n冇時間啦25號截止，極度要人幫手!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1782422\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1782422</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}